The [[switch police on|police]] force is mainly composed of angry dorks who dreamt of being in [[special forces]], failed all of the physicals, IQ tests, etc., and were faced with only one choice. Consumed by frustration, they have been beating up pretty much anyone they feel like for [[at least 100 years ago|at least 100 years]], but have recently become more advanced in their application of technology to the delicate art of doin' it to uppity [[hippy|hippies]], [[anarchy|anarchists]], and [[niggers]], most deserving every stroke of the night-stick they get. Where in the dark ages the police had to charge crowds with sabers drawn and slash and shoot the shit out of them, they now have tear gas, steel-plated fucking trucks and cool body armor. This constitutes a challenge for the rioter, especially as the body armor is now also flame-retardant, so plan carefully before your next riot. Otherwise the pigs will draw on their extensive training to fuck you up, [[Buttsex|manhandle you]] and most likely [[rape|pwn you thoroughly]] downtown.

